The Leader forces an ally to make every effort, increasing their characteristics by +<u>5+2×(Leader's FEL bonus)</u> for 1 round.{br}
Additionally, all of the Leader's abilities can be applied to the target of <b>Voice of Command</b> from any distance.{br}
A character who becomes the target of <b>Voice of Command</b> cannot be targeted by this ability again for the next 2 rounds.

The Leader forces an ally to fully push themselves, increasing their characteristics by +<u>(5 + 2 × Leader's FEL bonus)</u> for 1 round.{br}
Additionally, all of the Leader's abilities can be applied to the target of <b>Voice of Command</b> from any distance.{br}
A character who becomes the target of <b>Voice of Command</b> cannot be targeted by this ability again for the next 2 rounds.

